intelligence.

106
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:56,660
Drone swarms could change how wars are fought,

107
00:04:56,660 --> 00:05:00,610
and they and bring with them a lot of serious
ethical questions.

108
00:05:00,610 --> 00:05:02,889
For a drone swarm to be functional,

109
00:05:02,889 --> 00:05:06,300
the drones have to communicate with each other
in real time.

110
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:08,900
