human operator

111
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:10,690
wouldn't be able to manage.

112
00:05:10,690 --> 00:05:13,470
So individual drones need to be able to communicate

113
00:05:13,470 --> 00:05:16,350
with each other and make split second decisions

114
00:05:16,350 --> 00:05:17,350
as a group.

115
00:05:17,350 --> 00:05:19,699
Kind of like a school of fish.

116
00:05:19,699 --> 00:05:22,420
Fish equipped with bombs.

117
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:23,420
In other words,

118
00:05:23,420 --> 00:05:26,360
