00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:42,740
What if that drone is designed to fire a missile

126
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:44,360
or drop a bomb?

127
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,520
Will there be a human in a room somewhere

128
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,680
who makes that decision,

129
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:52,180
or will the drone make that call on its own?

130
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:55,090
Now this is a huge debate in the West.

131
00:05:55,090 --> 00:05:56,090
After all,

132
